SUMMARY:Oscars Watch Party at Buddies\, Diva
DESCRIPTION:Sunday\, March 15\, 2025  // 7pm // Doors 6pm\n$15 Advance // $20 Door\nall prices + fees\nBUY TICKETS \n\nHollywood’s biggest night… but make it drag. ✨ \nJoin us at Buddies for a full-glam Oscars Watch Party hosted by Canada’s Favourite Hole Vajayjay Abrams and Everybody’s Favourite Piece of Meat Miss Steak. \nWe’re rolling out the rainbow carpet for fierce red carpet commentary\, shady hot takes\, live reactions\, and big-screen viewing of every win\, snub\, and chaotic speech from the Academy Awards. \nStrut in your most iconic awards-season lewk for our Best Dressed Contest\, fill out an Oscars Ballot for your shot at prizes\, and stay for a drag show after the ceremony wraps. \nDoors at 6PM / Oscars at 7PM / Show after. \nLights. Camera. Camp. 🎬👑
URL:https://buddiesinbadtimes.com/event/oscars-watch-party-at-buddies-diva/
LOCATION:Tallulahs
END:VEVENT
