SUMMARY:Poetry Open Mic
DESCRIPTION:March 21\, 2026  // Sign Up + Doors 4pm // Showtime 4:30pm\nPWYC cash at the door\nBUY TICKETS \n \nJoin host Raymond Helkio for sassy poetry\, performance\, literature and libations! This month our featured artist is the wonderfully subversive performance artist and poet brawk hessel! This is an all-ages\, licensed PWYC event\, allies always welcome! Open mic slots are 3 minutes and if you’d like to read please sign-up at the door. \nSign-up + doors from 4:00 PM \nShowtime 4:30 PM \nBuddies is a fully accessible venue with barrier-free\, gender-neutral washrooms. Thank you to Jordyn Crawford\, Jonathan Freeman\, the staff at Buddies In Bad Times Theatre\, Tallulah’s Cabaret\, and The Reading Salon. MORE INFO: https://raymondhelkio.com/poetry-open-mic \nOther Dates:\nMarch 21\, 2026 | April 18\, 2026\nMay 16\, 2026 | June (TBA)
URL:https://buddiesinbadtimes.com/event/poetry-open-mic-17-2/
LOCATION:Tallulahs
END:VEVENT
