SUMMARY:Que'd Up presents: SHOP TALK - Live Event Lighting
DESCRIPTION:March 26\, 2026  // 6:30pm – 8:30pm // $20\nBUY TICKETS \n \nQue’d Up: Shop Talk workshop series returns on Thursday\, March 26th with a subject that has been very highly \nrequested: Lighting for Live Events! \nWe’ll be joined by Callum Sheedy (aka Jaw Jones) as our workshop facilitator\, who will go over various topics including: DMX\, understanding lighting fixtures\, consoles and softwares\, basic rigging\, light show programming and understanding conceptual approaches to lighting party spaces. \nThis workshop will take place at Buddies in Bad Times Theatre at 12 Alexander St. Tickets can be purchased in advance or at the door for this workshop\, however spots are limited so make sure to sign up at the link in our bio if you are interested in attending!
URL:https://buddiesinbadtimes.com/event/qued-up-presents-shop-talk-live-event-lighting/
LOCATION:Tallulahs
END:VEVENT
